{"tid":1785851,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"社長提前跑路果然是倒下了，《時光碎片》《為什麼老師會在這裡》製作公司破產","createTime":"2019-12-16T16:49:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-17T17:42:55.000Z","uid":75050,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"91cf4b9f3dd033016e7934ed5636e3c3700c68a5","tid":1785851,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T16:49:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hkacger.com/archives/94788/?\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkacger.com%2Farchives%2F94788%2F%3F&d=dVEf9brN%2BTtwApumOSMW7m0Q%2Fwx8zutUsTDhO6XOofs%3D&h=d5d53cb6\" target=\"_blank\">https://hkacger.com/archives/94788/?</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hkacger.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/00-35.jpg?\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkacger.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F12%2F00-35.jpg%3F&h=5877ca8b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>社長提前跑路果然是倒下了，《時光碎片》？《為什麼老師會在這裡》製作公司破產</ins></strong><br />\n作者：ACGER編輯部 日期： 16/12/2019<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hkacger.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/%E7%82%BA%E4%BB%80%E9%BA%BC%E8%80%81%E5%B8%AB%E6%9C%83%E5%9C%A8%E9%80%99%E8%A3%A1.png?\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkacger.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F12%2F%25E7%2582%25BA%25E4%25BB%2580%25E9%25BA%25BC%25E8%2580%2581%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%259C%25A8%25E9%2580%2599%25E8%25A3%25A1.png%3F&h=4684bae4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2019年12月16日更新：製作《為什麼老師會在這裡！？》《時光碎片》的動畫工作室Tear-studio，其公司ネクストバッターズサークル12月13日停止營業將申請破產<br />\n<br />\n公司事實在11月末已停止運作，同時公司代表亦無法聯絡，現時公司賠償支出大約4300萬日元，其中約800萬日元是約50位動畫製作者的未支付費用<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/YahooNewsTopics/status/1206447677862400001?\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FYahooNewsTopics%2Fstatus%2F1206447677862400001%3F&d=dVEf9brN%2BTtwApumOSMW7m0Q%2Fwx8zutUsTDhO6XOofs%3D&h=cec4b4cb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FYahooNewsTopics%2Fstatus%2F1206447677862400001%3F&h=7b7fece0\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/YahooNewsTopics/status/1206447677862400001?</a><br />\n<br />\n話說2019年4月福利番《為什麼老師會在這裡！？》的BD BOX今天（12月11日）發售<br />\n<br />\nBD BOX除了收錄電視動畫全12話的&ldquo;限界突破完全版&rdquo;，還有TV未放送的第13話<br />\n<br />\n日本網友對於此作BD順利發行都鬆一口氣能欣賞主角老師們的美妙乳首，其中保健老師立花千鶴的陷沒乳首看起來超可愛的<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hkacger.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/01-22-2048x570.jpg?\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkacger.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F12%2F01-22-2048x570.jpg%3F&h=3377ffbd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://blog-imgs-129.fc2.com/y/a/r/yarakan/SnapCrab_NoName_2019-12-10_8-55-49_No-00.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fblog-imgs-129.fc2.com%2Fy%2Fa%2Fr%2Fyarakan%2FSnapCrab_NoName_2019-12-10_8-55-49_No-00.jpg&d=dVEf9brN%2BTtwApumOSMW7m0Q%2Fwx8zutUsTDhO6XOofs%3D&h=2d05bc51\" target=\"_blank\">https://blog-imgs-129.fc2.com/y/a/r/yarakan/SnapCrab_NoName_2019-12-10_8-55-49_No-00.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hkacger.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/02-17-2048x578.jpg?\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkacger.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F12%2F02-17-2048x578.jpg%3F&h=b41d3808&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://blog-imgs-129.fc2.com/y/a/r/yarakan/SnapCrab_NoName_2019-12-10_8-56-12_No-00.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fblog-imgs-129.fc2.com%2Fy%2Fa%2Fr%2Fyarakan%2FSnapCrab_NoName_2019-12-10_8-56-12_No-00.jpg&d=dVEf9brN%2BTtwApumOSMW7m0Q%2Fwx8zutUsTDhO6XOofs%3D&h=3c710fa8\" target=\"_blank\">https://blog-imgs-129.fc2.com/y/a/r/yarakan/SnapCrab_NoName_2019-12-10_8-56-12_No-00.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hkacger.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/03-15-2048x572.jpg?\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkacger.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F12%2F03-15-2048x572.jpg%3F&h=bb3d5a8b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://blog-imgs-129.fc2.com/y/a/r/yarakan/SnapCrab_NoName_2019-12-10_9-6-27_No-00.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fblog-imgs-129.fc2.com%2Fy%2Fa%2Fr%2Fyarakan%2FSnapCrab_NoName_2019-12-10_9-6-27_No-00.jpg&d=dVEf9brN%2BTtwApumOSMW7m0Q%2Fwx8zutUsTDhO6XOofs%3D&h=f950ed2d\" target=\"_blank\">https://blog-imgs-129.fc2.com/y/a/r/yarakan/SnapCrab_NoName_2019-12-10_9-6-27_No-00.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hkacger.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/04-15-2048x574.jpg?\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkacger.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F12%2F04-15-2048x574.jpg%3F&h=a1c0a559&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://blog-imgs-129.fc2.com/y/a/r/yarakan/SnapCrab_NoName_2019-12-10_9-15-42_No-00.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fblog-imgs-129.fc2.com%2Fy%2Fa%2Fr%2Fyarakan%2FSnapCrab_NoName_2019-12-10_9-15-42_No-00.jpg&d=dVEf9brN%2BTtwApumOSMW7m0Q%2Fwx8zutUsTDhO6XOofs%3D&h=73056e9f\" target=\"_blank\">https://blog-imgs-129.fc2.com/y/a/r/yarakan/SnapCrab_NoName_2019-12-10_9-15-42_No-00.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hkacger.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/05-14-2048x578.jpg?\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkacger.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F12%2F05-14-2048x578.jpg%3F&h=377c6332&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://blog-imgs-129.fc2.com/y/a/r/yarakan/SnapCrab_NoName_2019-12-10_9-19-55_No-00.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fblog-imgs-129.fc2.com%2Fy%2Fa%2Fr%2Fyarakan%2FSnapCrab_NoName_2019-12-10_9-19-55_No-00.jpg&d=dVEf9brN%2BTtwApumOSMW7m0Q%2Fwx8zutUsTDhO6XOofs%3D&h=793764c2\" target=\"_blank\">https://blog-imgs-129.fc2.com/y/a/r/yarakan/SnapCrab_NoName_2019-12-10_9-19-55_No-00.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n為什麼說會&ldquo;鬆一口氣&rdquo;，是因為早兩天動畫製作者聲稱製作《為什麼老師會在這裡！？》的動畫公司Tear Studio<br />\n<br />\n欠薪被拖欠工資的苦主和知道內情的人士發聲，外部才發現Tear Studio的推特帳號已經消失，社長人都不見了疑似逃亡<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/GENP37/status/1203886678139523073?\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FGENP37%2Fstatus%2F1203886678139523073%3F&d=dVEf9brN%2BTtwApumOSMW7m0Q%2Fwx8zutUsTDhO6XOofs%3D&h=b7eade31\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FGENP37%2Fstatus%2F1203886678139523073%3F&h=7056c57d\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/GENP37/status/1203886678139523073?</a><br />\n<br />\n事緣動畫製作者佐藤元在推特披露有關Tear Studio未有支付製作者工資的消息<br />\n<br />\n其後有網友透露在打電話給Tear Studio查詢時，STAFF表示已有一陣子沒見過社長，疑似準備連夜逃亡<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hkacger.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/%E6%99%82%E5%85%89%E7%A2%8E%E7%89%87.jpg?\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkacger.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F08%2F%25E6%2599%2582%25E5%2585%2589%25E7%25A2%258E%25E7%2589%2587.jpg%3F&h=10e8457a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nTear Studio近期製作的動畫除了《為什麼老師會在這裡！？》還有劇場版《時光碎片》<br />\n<br />\n4月的《為什麼老師會在這裡！？》 BD還能順利發售，但11月才在日本上映的《時光碎片》情況就有些不妙了<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/HQVJF9/status/1203928747222556672?\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FHQVJF9%2Fstatus%2F1203928747222556672%3F&d=dVEf9brN%2BTtwApumOSMW7m0Q%2Fwx8zutUsTDhO6XOofs%3D&h=2a15b1df\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FHQVJF9%2Fstatus%2F1203928747222556672%3F&h=6a813073\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/HQVJF9/status/1203928747222556672?</a><br />\n<br />\n首先《時光碎片》本來預定在作品上映同時發行劇場限定BD，但在11月8日官方就宣布中止發行<br />\n<br />\n在《時光碎片》動畫官網12月10日的消息中，可意識到現在連製作委員會都找不到Tear Studio的代表負責人，搞不好《時光碎片》光碟會難產<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/jing_508/status/1204085179477708806?\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fjing_508%2Fstatus%2F1204085179477708806%3F&d=dVEf9brN%2BTtwApumOSMW7m0Q%2Fwx8zutUsTDhO6XOofs%3D&h=2782e662\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fjing_508%2Fstatus%2F1204085179477708806%3F&h=e681b584\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/jing_508/status/1204085179477708806?</a><br />\n<br />\n隨著事件發酵，有網友爆料稱Tear Studio在《為什麼老師會在這裡！？》的製作期間已經出現欠薪情況<br />\n<br />\n因為公司欠薪製作現場必然人手不足，當時願意留下來的STAFF是有價值與欠缺薪資的覺悟下進行動畫製作的<br />\n<br />\n而STAFF之所以一直沒說出來，是因為還有《時光碎片》等其他的作品需要製作<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>沒工資還繼續做動畫真的是用愛產生意志讓人相當敬佩，但某某這這就是在壓榨人材，這種風氣做法絕對不能助長</ins></strong>"},{"pid":"c1648f5557d435a805f49ed68f46d70025639cc1","tid":1785851,"uid":3747,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T17:37:25.000Z","msg":"欠薪都畫到咁高質<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f874600ab945a12a9e0f92a1c270352f0d0b487","tid":1785851,"uid":42340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T00:20:33.000Z","msg":"樓豬bye bye<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76c1ea06dd1456bd30946845bec932925ab6f947","tid":1785851,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2f874600ab945a12a9e0f92a1c270352f0d0b487","tid":1785851,"uid":42340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T00:20:33.000Z","msg":"樓豬bye bye<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T00:24:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10f0730754cb615f172a92fa777221d2089e75e4","tid":1785851,"uid":49130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T00:40:55.000Z","msg":"樓主rip<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efbcdac19bb56dc5e028b8f35fed6fdeb65f55f2","tid":1785851,"uid":53196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T05:21:16.000Z","msg":"多謝樓主"},{"pid":"2a8af7c4bb1e5c4569a3a3e29dbb1485c8ea6cec","tid":1785851,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"10f0730754cb615f172a92fa777221d2089e75e4","tid":1785851,"uid":49130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T00:40:55.000Z","msg":"樓主rip<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T10:58:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35731e58c198a9fcc0564f2af0d295813fdf633e","tid":1785851,"uid":44718,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T11:01:51.000Z","msg":"我仲以為「社長提前跑路果然是倒下了」係啲咩新動畫名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f302c56f05f5dc33990a07c9ff00e4dd9f13a622","tid":1785851,"uid":138967,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T11:05:17.000Z","msg":"《為什麼社長會走佬了? 》係咪續集黎?"},{"pid":"eb255257604d372c5ff163d678207199c20cd571","tid":1785851,"uid":30510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T11:40:44.000Z","msg":"鬼之兒嶋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60cc4944f916d12c91c243169d31cc51e6199324","tid":1785851,"uid":49995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T14:34:32.000Z","msg":"時光沙漏 嘉禾會上喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aec83b38d64f0baa3cdf953326e02f1697e16326","tid":1785851,"uid":2002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T14:36:45.000Z","msg":"畫到a1咁咪唔會執囉"},{"pid":"1bc899c83c576f9833e04518ae7c4a42e7b645d8","tid":1785851,"uid":73627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T15:34:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />樓主"},{"pid":"3d15b71f1462422d41e3136f450b7a79ca6b3549","tid":1785851,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1bc899c83c576f9833e04518ae7c4a42e7b645d8","tid":1785851,"uid":73627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T15:34:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />樓主"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T16:42:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bf196c02eea7655ddcefb1813e79a7088b116a4","tid":1785851,"uid":224429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T17:42:55.000Z","msg":"垃圾社長夾帶私逃<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}